trans-unit.source: Interacts with the parser to build a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.LinkButton"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: 分析器以生成与交互<xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.LinkButton"></xref>控件。

trans-unit.source: The LinkButtonControlBuilder causes the parser to ignore inner text if it is completely made up of white space characters.
trans-unit.target: LinkButtonControlBuilder 使分析器忽略内部文本，如果完全由构成的空白字符。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.LinkButtonControlBuilder"></xref> class.
Specifies whether white space literals are allowed.
trans-unit.target: 指定是否允许存在空白。

trans-unit.source: This method overrides <xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder.AllowWhitespaceLiterals%2A?displayProperty=fullName> to ignore white space in the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LinkButton> control.
trans-unit.target: 此方法将替代<xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder.AllowWhitespaceLiterals%2A?displayProperty=fullName>若要忽略中的白色空间<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LinkButton>控件。</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LinkButton> </xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder.AllowWhitespaceLiterals%2A?displayProperty=fullName>
